org.eclipse.cdt.core.dom.ast

Interface IASTFieldDeclarator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASTAttributeOwner, IASTDeclarator, IASTNameOwner, IASTNode
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICPPASTFieldDeclarator

    public interface IASTFieldDeclarator
extends IASTDeclarator
    This represents a field in a struct. This allows for the specification of size for a bit field.

        IASTFieldDeclarator copy()

         copy.getParent() == null
 copy.getPropertyInParent() == null
 copy.isFrozen() == false
        Preprocessor nodes do not currently support being copied. Implicit name nodes are not copied, instead they can be regenerated if required.

        Calling this method is equivalent to copy(CopyStyle.withoutLocations).
